ogn med en mobiltelefon i h\u00e5nda, i stedet for \u00e5 forholde seg til barnet, sier Hagen."]}, {"field": "category0", "value": "pluss"}, {"field": "contenthash", "value": "487852c524986db627c5a613b586f3f19f5ab6d1b693b54e603fd0e76c4eea58"}, {"field": "createtime", "value": "2016-02-04T06:33:23.000Z"}, {"field": "description", "value": "Mobilen \u00abstjeler\u00bb tid vi kunne brukt p\u00e5 andre ting, danner nye normer for kommunikasjon og forstyrrer samtaler. Samtidig er den en stor ressurs."}, {"field": "dominantimage", "value": "http://www.adressa.no/incoming/article12110290.ece/men75g/ALTERNATES/w980-default/doc6nsyi39lx861gnqk13bp.jpg"}, {"field": "dominantimagedimensions", "value": "980x551"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnail", "value": "http://content-thumbnail.cxpublic.com/content/dominantthumbnail/1d6a2f4ded4dcf46492a17c1d7d5ab1d776d24ea.jpg?596a8414"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnaildimensions", "value": "300x169"}, {"field": "heading", "value": ["Slik p\u00e5virker mobilen hverdagen -adressa.no", "- N\u00e5 g\u00e5r vi rett p\u00e5", "- Vi m\u00e5 styre teknologien", "Mobilfrie soner"]}, {"field": "id", "value": "1d6a2f4ded4dcf46492a17c1d7d5ab1d776d24ea"}, {"field": "keyword", "value": ["pluss", "eadressa", "ukeadressa", "digitalt", "arkiv", "fordeler"]}, {"field": "keywords", "value": "pluss,eadressa,ukeadressa,digitalt,arkiv,fordeler"}, {"field": "kw-category", "value": "pluss"}, {"field": "kw-classification", "value": "technology-and-computing"}, {"field": "kw-company", "value": "facebook"}, {"field": "kw-concept", "value": ["mobil", "l\u00e6re barn", "p\u00e5virker mobilen hverdagen", "teknologi", "bruk", "p\u00e5virker mobilen", "mobilen hverdagen"]}, {"field": "kw-entity", "value": ["medie-norge", "snapchat", "internett", "adresseavisen", "hoeggen"]}, {"field": "kw-location", "value": ["gallup", "trondheim", "oslo"]}, {"field": "kw-pageclass", "value": "article"}, {"field": "kw-person", "value": ["berit skog", "ingunn hagen"]}, {"field": "kw-taxonomy", 